  "texts": [
    "Knowing the significance of training in ML will enable the system to collect the appropriate volume and quality of training data for the model.",
    "Once the system knows how it affects model prediction and why it's essential, it can choose the optimal algorithm based on the availability and suitability of the training data set [112].",
    "Machine learning and its algorithmsThe ML algorithm enables the ML model to perceive the input data in a particular manner.",
    "The training process is the sole method that interoperates with ML algorithms so that ML models can extract meaningful information from learning data.",
    "It might take time to find an algorithm that works well and is set up to meet the needs of the intended use in a particular domain."
